00:16:48,549 --> 00:16:50,634
The location's great, vibe is great.

357
00:16:50,718 --> 00:16:53,178
- Did you see the face she made?
- I saw it.

358
00:16:53,262 --> 00:16:55,556
<i>When she squinted her eyes</i>
<i>to take the photo,</i>

359
00:16:55,639 --> 00:16:57,641
