739
00:34:10,506 --> 00:34:11,924
And then after that,

740
00:34:13,593 --> 00:34:15,344
if you still think you like me,

741
00:34:15,428 --> 00:34:17,555
then I'd want you to ask me out.
I'd like that.

742
00:34:22,935 --> 00:34:24,395
I won't give up on you.

743
00:34:32,195 --> 00:34:33,154
I understand.

744
00:34:34,989 --> 00:34:38,910
Even after all of this is over,
and we all go our separate ways in life,

745
00:34:38,993 --> 00:34:40,203
I feel like…

746
00:34:42,538 --> 00:34:44,749
one day, you might have a change of heart,

747
00:34:45,416 --> 00:34:48,127
and develop feelings for me.
I still have hope.

748
00:34:48,795 --> 00:34:50,755
So, I think I'll want to keep

749
00:34:50,838 --> 00:34:52,799
fighting for you and not give up.

750
00:34:54,926 --> 00:34:56,636
Maybe that will motivate me

751
00:34:57,136 --> 00:34:58,971
to work even harder at my job.

752
00:34:59,055 --> 00:35:00,515
To be honest, I don't know.

753
00:35:04,310 --> 00:35:05,561
I'm glad that

754
00:35:06,104 --> 00:35:07,271
I was

755
00:35:07,355 --> 00:35:09,107
able to fall in love

756
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:10,274
with someone.

757
00:35:10,358 --> 00:35:12,151
I don't want to give up on that.

758
00:35:14,987 --> 00:35:15,905
So, yeah.

759
00:35:18,407 --> 00:35:21,077
I said I wouldn't cry, but I did anyway.

760
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:22,662
It's okay to cry.

761
00:35:22,745 --> 00:35:24,705
You can't avoid it.

762
00:35:28,918 --> 00:35:30,878
I get it. Thank you.

763
00:35:30,962 --> 00:35:32,296
I'm not gonna give up.

764
00:35:39,762 --> 00:35:41,722
- Thanks again.
- Bye.

765
00:35:55,403 --> 00:35:57,321
You're being kinda sweet right now.

766
00:35:57,405 --> 00:35:59,407
